'''天主教阿爾巴諾羅馬城郊教區'''（{{lang-la|Dioecesis Albanensis}}）是一個羅馬天主教的[[羅馬城郊教區|羅馬城郊教區]]。

教區於2011年時有470,300名教友（佔轄區總人口93%）、77個堂區、184名司鐸、43名終身執事、146名修士和1,110名修女。

該教區除了本身的教區主教外，亦有一位領此主教銜的[[樞機#位階|主教級樞機]]；不過後者只是在名義上以該主教為領銜，並沒有管理該教區的實權。現任教區主教為{{link-en|才祿·塞梅拉羅|Marcello Semeraro}}<ref>{{cite press release |title=RINUNCE E NOMINE, 01.10.2004 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2004/10/01/0477/01216.html |publisher=Sala Stampa della Santa Sede |accessdate=2020-02-26 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200226163034/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2004/10/01/0477/01216.html |archivedate=2020-02-26 |language=it |date=2004-10-01 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，榮休輔理主教為{{link-de|保祿·吉萊特|Paolo Gillet}}<ref>{{cite press release |title=RINUNCE E NOMINE, 22.02.2005 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2005/02/22/0101/00247.html |publisher=Sala Stampa della Santa Sede |accessdate=2020-02-26 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200226164932/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2005/02/22/0101/00247.html |archivedate=2020-02-26 |language=it |date=2005-02-22 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，領銜主教為[[安傑洛·索達諾|安傑洛·索達諾]]樞機<ref>{{cite web |last1=Miranda |first1=Salvador |title=Suburbicarian Dioceses and Cardinal Patriarchs of Oriental Rite |url=https://webdept.fiu.edu/~mirandas/sub-sees.htm |publisher=Florida International University |accessdate=2020-02-26 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200226165310/https://webdept.fiu.edu/~mirandas/sub-sees.htm |archivedate=2020-02-26 |language=en |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

